{"title":"最大子段和","time_limit":233,"memory_limit":64,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/563#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=563","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/563/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/563/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/563"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"### ~~这是一道水题~~\r\n\r\n现在某只很懒的动物遇到了一个难题\r\n\r\n已知有 $T$ 个序列\r\n\r\n每个序列由 $ni$ 个数字构成\r\n\r\n现在它需要找到每个序列的最大子段和\r\n\r\n但是这只懒惰的动物想去睡会儿觉，于是它请你帮帮它。\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行 ： $T$\r\n\r\n接下来有 $T$ 组数据\r\n\r\n 每组数据 ：\r\n-    第一行 ： 一个 $n$ 表示这个序列有 $n$ 个数\r\n\r\n- 接下来 一行 $n$ 个 $ai$"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出 $T$ 行\r\n\r\n每行为每个序列的最大子段和"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入\r\n\r\n```cpp\r\n2\r\n4\r\n2 3 3 3\r\n4\r\n-5 6 -5 10\r\n```\r\n\r\n输出\r\n```cpp\r\n11\r\n11\r\n```\r\n"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"- $T$ $<=$ $30$\r\n\r\n- $n$ $<=$ $10^4$\r\n\r\n- $-1,000$ $<=$ $ai$ $<= $ $1000$\r\n\r\n\r\n- 注意 子段必须是连续的一段，且子段长度至少为 $1$\r\n\r\n- 注意 时限"}]}